defaultReports
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
defaultCommittees should keep their reports short and accessible, and avoid too many recommendations (para 79).default&#xa0;defaultCommittees should clearly indicate which recommendations are most important (which will help the committee achieve impact and make follow-up easier) and to whom each recommendation is addressed (para 79).default&#xa0;
